The evidence with the title 'Why not raise the minimum wage to $100 an hour? ' says Dec 10, 2013  ... During his speech calling for wage hikes , Obama claimed the minimum wage, “ in real terms right now is below where it was when Harry Truman was in office . ”Yet the non - partisan site PolitiFact.com found Obama 's claim applied to just one year of Truman 's eight - yearpresidency ( thesixthyear,1950).
